    "description": "ChatGPT just killed the “I don’t have time” excuse.\n\nGo to chatgpt.com/agents → Create an Agent → describe the job in plain language.\n\nNo code. No prompts. No Zapier.\n\nIt maps the steps, connects your tools, and runs in the cloud while you sleep.\n\nOne team built a sales agent that researches accounts, summarizes calls, and posts deal briefs into Slack automatically — 5 hours of work a week, gone.\n\nThis is what AI automation actually looks like. Not chat.\n\nComment “agent” and I’ll DM you the link\n#aiagents #chatgpt #aiautomation",
